Ecco una landing page single-file in stile cyberpunk per un negozio di programmazione AI, con modulo contatti e popup di conferma.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.1">
    <title>AI Code Store - CyberPunk</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset base */
        @import url('https://googlefonts.com/cyber-sair-display&subset=latin');
        * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: 'Cyber', sans-serif;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
        background: #000;
        color: #lime;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20rem 2rem;
        background: radial-gradient circle at 50% 50%, #0f0 0, #000 70%;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        width: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        border: 2px solid #0f0;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40px #0f0, inset 0 0 40px #0f0;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 2px dashed #0f0;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px #0f0, 0 0 20px #0f0;
        letter-spacing:  -0.2em;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .sub-title {
        color: #0f0;
        opacity: 0.8;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-top: -0.5rem;
    }

    .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr);
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }

    .card {
        background: #000;
        border: 1px solid #0f0;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px #0f0 inset;
        transition: 0.3s;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0f0, inset 0 0 20px #0f0;
    }

    .card h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .price {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #0f0;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #0f0;
    }

    .btn {
        background: #0f0;
        color: #000;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 0;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: 0.3s;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px #0f0;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background: #fff;
        color: #000;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0f0;
    }

    .form-group {
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    input, textarea {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        background: #000;
        border: 1px solid #0f0;
        color: #0f0;
        font-size: 1rem;
        outline: none;
        transition: 0.3s;
    }

    input:focus, textarea:focus {
        border-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px #0f0;
    }

    label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        color: #0f0;
        text-shadow: 0 0 2px #0f0;
    }

    .footer {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px dashed #0f0;
        padding-top: 1rem;
    }

    .popup-over {
        display: none;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.0);
        z-index: 100;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    }

    .popup-over.show {
        display: flex;
    }

    .popup-box {
        background: #000;
        border: 2px solid #0f0;
        padding: 2rem 3rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 40px #0f0;
        text-align: center;
        animation: flick 1.2;
    }

    .popup-box h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .popup-box .btn {
        width: auto;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    @keyframes flick {
        0% { opacity: 0; filter: blur(10px); }
        100% { opacity: 1; filter: blur(0px); }
    }

    .globe {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #0f0;
        opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .code {
        background: #0f0;
        color: #000;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
        font-family: monospace;
    }

    .error {
        border-color: red;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px red;
    }

    .error-m {
        color: red;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        margin-top: 0.2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .container {
        padding: 1rem;
    }
    }
</style>
</head>
